articles.title: US vetoes UN resolution calling for immediate ceasefire in Gaza after proposing a temporary halt in fighting - CNN
articles.description: The United States has vetoed a resolution at the United Nations calling for an immediate ceasefire in Gaza, an anticipated move that, while supportive of Israel, comes amid signs of American frustration with Israel’s war.
